snippet.title: COMPLETE tape recording of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard from 2015 - Part 1
snippet.description:
First part of the complete tape recording of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard from 2015 which was submitted and played at Britain’s High Court in London during Depp’s libel case against The Sun newspaper.

Part 2: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IGmC0NSEuWQ

Source: https://www.courttv.com/news/amber-heard-witness-statements-depp-blamed-the-monster-for-physical-verbal-abuse/

All court documents from the UK court case can be found here: https://www.nickwallis.com/depp-trial
